  title: "Update on the Godot Game",
  pubDate: "22/04/2025",
};
---
<MarkdownPostLayout {...frontmatter}>
    <p>I've been debating what my game should be about. Aside from being a 2D game with pixel art, I haven't made any concrete decisions yet.
